quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"Saad. Mi woondirii Alqur'aana, jom waaju"
  38,2,"Si ko woni, yeddu…ďe …ďen wonii e townitaare e lurral"
  38,3,"∆äuu…óii e gire …óen Men halki, ado ma…ď…ďe, …ďen noddi faabo, kono tawi ko bonatno bonii"
  38,4,"∆Āe Ňčal…ói, nde jertinoowo jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, arata …ďe. Yeddu…ďe …ďen wi'i: \"Oo, ko mbileejo heewu…óo fenaande"
  38,5,"Kere o wa…óay rewetee…ói …óin, rewetee…óo gooto? Pellet, …óum ko huunde haawniinde non"
  38,6,"Mbatu ma…ď…ďe ngun huccitiri wiide: \"Yehee, tabiton e rewetee…ói mon …óin. ∆äum …óoo, ko huunde e…ď…ďanaande"
  38,7,"Men nanaali fii …óum, e diina sakkitiika kan. ∆äum wonaali, si wanaa ko fefindaa"
  38,8,"Kere ko e makko Jantoore nden jippotoo hakkunde amen?\" Si ko woni, …ďe wonii e sikkitagol Jantoore Am nden. Wurin, ko fii …ďe mee…óaali taho, lepte Am …óen"
  38,9,"Kaa …ďe jogiti ngaluuji yurmeende Joomi maa, Foolu…óo, Dokko On"
  38,10,Kaa ko kam…ďe woodani laamagol kammuli …óin e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji? Haray yo …ďe ∆īeenŇču …ďe ∆īawa
  38,11,"Ko …ďe konu hoyngu non, fooleteengu e feddeeji …óin"
  38,12,"Ado ma…ď…ďe, yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen fennuno, e Aadi'en e Fir'awna jom-peme"
  38,13,"e Samuuda'en, e yim…ďe Luutu …ďen, e yim…ďe pitaaji …ďen; ko …ďen woni feddeeji (fennu…ďe) …ďen"
  38,14,"Kala …ďee wonaali, si wanaa o fennii Nulaa…ďe …ďen. Lepte Am …óen jojji e ma…ď…ďe"
  38,15,"∆Āee habbaaki, si wanaa haacaango gooto, ngo alaa ruttorde"
  38,16,"∆Āe wi': \"Joomi amen, yaccinan men ge…ďal lepte amen, ado √Ďalaande hasboore nden"
